She smiles at Alysia. ~We had just chased out a barbaric male, followed by an ignorant one, and then another man walked in and started yelling about the service. Naturally, I assumed he was being rude... how was I to know he was joking around?~<br>
<br>
She turns back to Dawn. ~Of course I would have kind words for your son, if he had kind words for me. Male or female, I react to people's personalities... a rude greeting gets a rude response, it's nothing to do with gender. However, any Amazon in high stature I would respect whether they were rude or not. I know how the hierarchy works, I'm not in fantasy of being queen. I give each person the respect they deserve.~<br>
<br>
